name: Custom Vinyl Spoke Cards
description: These spoke cards are printed on a rigid vinyl and UV coated, which means they are 100% sun and water proof. These cards were made for The Denver Spoke (RIP) as a punch card for tube changes in the shop. Send a vector file/graphics you would like printed, or choose from one of our designs, and we'll have them shipped out to you in about 2 weeks. Come in sets of 50.
